msgid "KSystemLog"
msgstr "KSystemLog"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.ksystemlog.appdata.xml:7
msgid "system log viewer"
msgstr "penampil catatan log sistem"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ksystemlog.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"KSystemLog show all logs of your system, grouped by General (Default system "
"log, Authentication, Kernel, X.org...), and optional Services (Apache, Cups, "
"etc, ...). It includes many features to read nicely your log files:"
msgstr ""
"KSystemLog menampilkan semua catatan log sistemmu, dikelompokkan berdasarkan "
"General (Catatan log sistem baku, Autentikasi, Kernel, X.org...), dan "
"Layanan (Apache, Cups, dll, ...) opsional. Serta banyak fitur-fitur "
"pembacaan secara baik file-file catatan log-mu:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.ksystemlog.appdata.xml:13
msgid "Colorize log lines depending on their severities"
msgstr "Pewarnaan baris log tergantung pada kepelikannya"

